Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.30,0:01:37.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.82,0:01:39.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To school.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.30,0:01:41.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A place for studying?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.01,0:01:44.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. Other than Saturdays, I go almost every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.67,0:01:49.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't follow me, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.32,0:01:49.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsk.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.68,0:01:50.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with that tongue clicking?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.16,0:01:53.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm bored.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.08,0:01:54.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Watch TV then.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.65,0:01:56.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be going then.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.73,0:02:03.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An era where only studying is required of children?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.21,0:02:05.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This has become a fine country.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.64,0:02:14.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsugumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.09,0:02:16.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Jin!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.44,0:02:17.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.05,0:02:22.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How is Nagi-san? Is she all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.90,0:02:24.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, so-so.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.62,0:02:26.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's at home now?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.17,0:02:28.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about school?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.93,0:02:31.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll think about it after I get in touch with my old man.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.47,0:02:35.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for the side dishes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.05,0:02:37.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll return the tupperware at school.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.83,0:02:39.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.60,0:02:41.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.51,0:02:44.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which ones were delicious?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.33,0:02:47.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All of them were delicious... Especially...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.69,0:02:50.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The fried vegetables were delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.52,0:02:51.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.61,0:02:53.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,School... huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.88,0:03:10.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That color is no good.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.59,0:03:12.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The harmony is all messed up.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.30,0:03:15.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've lost your sense of direction.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.97,0:03:18.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What exactly are you trying to portray?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.73,0:03:23.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When your design is slipshod, using eccentric colors isn't going to help.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.71,0:03:27.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've already said you're not up to oil painting yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.30,0:03:30.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mikuriya, this is still {you're doing something }beyond your ability. {shorten?}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.40,0:03:33.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a waste of time, taking out so many painting equipments.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.14,0:03:34.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your palette is full of paint too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.05,0:03:36.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.70,0:03:38.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know I suck, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.87,0:03:40.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.59,0:03:41.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.20,0:03:44.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You just want to imitate him, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.60,0:03:54.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's completed!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.89,0:03:58.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The rookie of the Arts Club, Daitetsu-kun has finished his oil painting!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.47,0:04:03.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing! To finish a painting with only a palette knife, that's so cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.33,0:04:05.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A person with a large-build sure has a bold style!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.26,0:04:08.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But there's a calculated beauty even beneath the boldness!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.29,0:04:11.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That pink highlight is effective.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.73,0:04:14.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sense is needed to use pink effectively.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.76,0:04:15.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jin...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.23,0:04:19.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How's the sculpture?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.30,0:04:24.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry. It was somewhat completed, but I broke it by accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.62,0:04:27.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry you had to carry the tree for me...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.21,0:04:29.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.89,0:04:32.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to lend you this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.66,0:04:37.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's... very cute...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.10,0:04:39.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whenever I think about it,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.78,0:04:41.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I... I...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.85,0:04:42.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.11,0:04:45.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm trying to work here, so shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.55,0:04:47.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now the focus line I've drawn is off! {err... focus line... it's for drawing attention to the main character}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.05,0:04:50.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh my, Akiba-kun. You're here?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.06,0:04:52.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am. I've been here all along.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.93,0:04:55.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were so quiet, I didn't notice you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.57,0:04:57.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So... How's your comic coming along?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.61,0:04:59.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't change the topic.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.49,0:05:01.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well... it's moving steadily.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.10,0:05:03.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your work's still as good.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.01,0:05:04.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for your compliment.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.69,0:05:06.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which magazine are you submitting to this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.84,0:05:08.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Monthly Issue Dejavu.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.39,0:05:12.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you mean that magazine full of comics that I thought I've seen before.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.87,0:05:16.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But this comic sure gives the feeling of "What exactly is going on?" {rephrase?}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.86,0:05:19.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The motive of the war is unclear, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.16,0:05:23.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The world-view is influenced by existing works. There's no originality.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.28,0:05:25.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you some examiner from a comic school?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.82,0:05:28.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you come to the Arts Club anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.36,0:05:30.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you want to draw comics, you should've gone to the Comics Club.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.63,0:05:31.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Comics Club?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.05,0:05:36.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't group me with the likes of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.33,0:05:40.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They talk about anime wherever they go, and they even don't care about their attire!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.32,0:05:44.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In any case, from what I've seen from their doujinshi, they're hardly active at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.10,0:05:48.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you have no interest in anime and such, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.13,0:05:49.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like Lolikko Cutie.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.28,0:05:54.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, That's actually a magical girl show that's entirely different from other anime.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.56,0:05:57.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Especially in that episode with the collaboration of Director Yajima and Hashida-san,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.10,0:05:59.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the quality is comparable to a movie's, and the direction is targeted at adults.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.97,0:06:03.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Only that episode is sold well on DVD, the related merchandise is also highly appraised.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.53,0:06:04.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.60,0:06:06.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think, Shino?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.32,0:06:08.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think it's great.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.42,0:06:12.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Considering the Arts Club tends to have few male members...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.26,0:06:14.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,our first-year students this year can be called a good harvest.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.09,0:06:16.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A hulk of an artist.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.14,0:06:18.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Too-pure-pure-boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.59,0:06:20.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A self-conscious Akiba-freak.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.09,0:06:23.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you think it's a terrific balance?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.56,0:06:26.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If this is an RPG, they can form a party and fight a boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.89,0:06:29.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takako, which boy do you prefer?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.36,0:06:32.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see... it's hard to rule out any of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.86,0:06:33.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if I have to choose...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.44,0:06:35.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Too-pure-pure boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.25,0:06:38.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Both Akiba and Daitetsu are amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.65,0:06:43.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't create a piece of art on my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.39,0:06:46.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jin, you're also trying your best.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.80,0:06:50.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I entered the Arts Club because I look up to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.48,0:06:52.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I may be hopeless now...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.62,0:06:55.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But someday I will surpass you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.27,0:07:00.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This... This is it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.48,0:07:04.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Friendship and rivalry! Too-pure-pure-boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.53,0:07:05.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takako, your nosebleed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.08,0:07:07.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, a boss fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.19,0:07:11.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, as they say, youngsters need a trial.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.05,0:07:13.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tidy the storehouse?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.63,0:07:18.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right. In the northwest of the school compounds, there's an old building for hobby groups.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.47,0:07:21.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The basement there is used as a storehouse for the Arts Club.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.54,0:07:25.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been deserted for years, so I'd like to tidy it up before I step down.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.32,0:07:28.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fortunately, we have male helpers this year.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.82,0:07:31.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Old building for hobby groups... you don't mean that one, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.25,0:07:34.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh sheesh, you know already.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.12,0:07:36.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean, that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.40,0:07:38.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.08,0:07:40.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll pass! Definitely a pass!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.09,0:07:42.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Mikuriya, you're afraid of ghosts?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.06,0:07:44.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's actually the opposite.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.41,0:07:46.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's really good with ghosts.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.06,0:07:47.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to go!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.38,0:07:49.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like I can do anything even if I can see them!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.72,0:07:52.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We keep going to temples and such during field trips, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.06,0:07:54.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not fun at all! It's not fun at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.56,0:07:57.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something amazing will happen if you tell him ghost stories.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.20,0:07:58.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no joke.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.55,0:07:59.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh my.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.51,0:08:01.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I never thought we'd have this kind of talent.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.94,0:08:05.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've always wanted to ask you something, Jin.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.02,0:08:10.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What will happen if a ghost meets a netted door? {or screen door? it's a door for keeping out mosquitos}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.18,0:08:12.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Netted door?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.00,0:08:13.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can it pass through?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.02,0:08:17.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.63,0:08:19.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.71,0:08:22.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the first time I'm seeing it up close.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.74,0:08:24.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I usually won't come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.82,0:08:28.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't look straight and walk. Somebody, guide me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.48,0:08:29.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you bringing me along?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.03,0:08:31.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, let's go inside first.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.07,0:08:33.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Today we'll just look around.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.65,0:08:37.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we don't see what's inside, we won't know how many helpers we'll need.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.46,0:08:37.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}I'm sorry, I'm really sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.03,0:08:39.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}I was born like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.06,0:08:40.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}I'm really sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.20,0:08:40.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jin... It's hard to walk.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.13,0:08:43.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Akiba-kun, you look relaxed.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.27,0:08:45.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't believe in ghosts.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.14,0:08:52.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This place's got the atmosphere. A single naked light bulb? {lol, naked?}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.16,0:08:56.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, let's move those obstructions so that we can carry stuff easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.44,0:08:57.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Daitetsu, your back is so big.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.78,0:08:59.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you come here for?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.75,0:09:03.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look, this is just a musty storehouse.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.31,0:09:05.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The ghost thing is just a rumor.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.91,0:09:08.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.30,0:09:14.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's even a storage under the floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.87,0:09:17.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This will take more work than expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.43,0:09:20.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.14,0:09:23.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard this from Senpai just now...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.27,0:09:27.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's true that there was an accident here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.46,0:09:33.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's real. A student fell down from a ladder and died.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.29,0:09:37.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There happened to be a sharp pole right below.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.56,0:09:41.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was impaled, but he remained conscious for a short while.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.74,0:09:44.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He cried for help, but nobody came.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.07,0:09:46.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Around him, a sea of blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.54,0:09:50.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the meantime, he bled until he lost all his strength...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.03,0:09:55.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But that student has not realized that he's dead...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.05,0:09:59.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even now, you can still hear him calling for help...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.79,0:10:04.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Liar! You see, there's no ladder around here!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.62,0:10:05.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.08,0:10:07.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't the ladder here?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.41,0:10:26.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, have you tidied up the place?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.32,0:10:29.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm telling the truth!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.70,0:10:31.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I really heard something!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.25,0:10:34.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're so useless. You should find the cause of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.48,0:10:35.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you a beast?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.75,0:10:39.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Let's look at this shop's specialty: the crab ice-cream!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.91,0:10:43.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Its sale is limited to fifty per day, so it'll be sold out in a jiffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.22,0:10:46.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could that be an impurity?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.20,0:10:48.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Should I tell Nagi?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.14,0:10:52.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do I do? Because if I tell her...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.21,0:10:54.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to go to the school too!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.55,0:10:56.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She'll definitely say that!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.20,0:10:58.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter, Jin?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.63,0:10:59.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You look down.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.72,0:11:03.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.81,0:11:04.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.09,0:11:06.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you troubled over something?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.54,0:11:08.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's really nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.29,0:11:10.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This worry has nothing to do with you at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.69,0:11:12.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.55,0:11:19.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}I tried doing it one more time, but it still stinks.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.97,0:11:22.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can I hold an impurity in my hand and bring it home?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.83,0:11:25.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How about putting it in a bottle... That won't work.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.00,0:11:27.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I still can't be sure it was caused by an impurity...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.65,0:11:28.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Mikuriya!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.91,0:11:31.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mikuriya!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.02,0:11:34.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry. My emotions got the better of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.38,0:11:37.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of monster are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.23,0:11:39.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not satisfied with a pretty childhood friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.87,0:11:40.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.92,0:11:42.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm convinced now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.67,0:11:45.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If this world is a comic, you are the main character.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.26,0:11:47.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shall I carry your bag for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.74,0:11:49.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, but it's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.32,0:11:52.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That side is the courtyard, and if you go this way, there's a stadium.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.32,0:11:53.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is such a lively place.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.27,0:11:55.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's such a beauty!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.78,0:11:59.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Her head is so small! Her legs are long! Her hair is so silky!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.00,0:12:02.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do we have such a beauty in our school?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.28,0:12:03.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't she a transfer student?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.66,0:12:05.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At this time of semester?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.25,0:12:09.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jin-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.38,0:12:17.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jin-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.21,0:12:24.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He dodged!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.23,0:12:25.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He dodged the hug!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.64,0:12:28.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't he the guy that Nagi-san was looking for?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.63,0:12:32.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're so mean, Jin-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.33,0:12:33.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.09,0:12:35.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't "why" me. In any case, your character is gross, so stop it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.66,0:12:36.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did he just say gross?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.05,0:12:38.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This guy is impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.53,0:12:41.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He has two ahoge, so he's an idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.04,0:12:42.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In English, Aho-Aho-Man, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.75,0:12:43.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He may be a homo.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.00,0:12:46.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me, but I'm her relative.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.24,0:12:49.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like what you're thinking. Sorry, I'm really sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.20,0:13:04.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing, Nagi-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.01,0:13:06.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me, what do you mean I'm gross?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.55,0:13:08.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why the hell did you come to school?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.82,0:13:11.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why? Hah, you have the cheek to ask. {a ch33kster pun}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.49,0:13:12.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know you're hiding something from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.53,0:13:14.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How did you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.62,0:13:16.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? So it's true?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.04,0:13:17.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? You tricked me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.02,0:13:21.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard from Tsugumi that there's a commotion concerning ghosts.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.40,0:13:24.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope I guessed wrong...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.80,0:13:25.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.76,0:13:27.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you saw an impurity, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.68,0:13:30.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I saw it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.76,0:13:32.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.01,0:13:34.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My eyes never err. {I think cow needs TLC on this line lol}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.24,0:13:38.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I sense the presence of an impurity here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.01,0:13:41.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They appear easily at a place with many people.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.43,0:13:48.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.11,0:13:49.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsugumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.45,0:13:53.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nagi-san, I told you not to wander around on your own!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.30,0:13:56.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, I'm a curious person.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.47,0:14:00.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'd be troublesome if people find out you're an outsider.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.17,0:14:02.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You already stand out without doing anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.33,0:14:06.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsugumi, are you the one who brought her along?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.79,0:14:08.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because when I was going home...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.67,0:14:10.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I found Nagi-san clinging onto the school gates.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.54,0:14:13.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nagi-san told me she always had a private tutor,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.55,0:14:15.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so she has never gone to school bofore.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.48,0:14:18.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't stand out if I enter the school in school uniform, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.71,0:14:21.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what she said...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.10,0:14:23.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So we went home and I lent her a set of uniform.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.03,0:14:26.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You did something daring.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.00,0:14:29.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you have spares?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.00,0:14:32.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our school is a private school, so the uniforms are expensive.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.50,0:14:36.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah! That's because girls are concerned about uniforms.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.74,0:14:42.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't tell him that I got fatter during the spring break and the size doesn't fit anymore, so I bought another set!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.38,0:14:46.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On top of that, that size fits Nagi-san perfectly!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.05,0:14:47.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't bring myself to say it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.60,0:14:49.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's how it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.21,0:14:52.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsugumi-san is such a gentle and kind person!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.77,0:14:54.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're now really close!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.77,0:14:56.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, Tsugumi-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.65,0:14:59.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, we became good friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.69,0:15:04.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was wrong about you. You're more easygoing than I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.73,0:15:07.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think you should call her easygoing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.44,0:15:08.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's just selfish.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.56,0:15:09.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Mikuriya.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.44,0:15:12.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you done with the talking?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.08,0:15:15.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can we join in?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.21,0:15:18.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So who is that person?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.15,0:15:23.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This girl is my half-sibling, born from a different mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.71,0:15:27.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She ran away from home and now she's staying at my house.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.28,0:15:27.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.23,0:15:29.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nagi-san. {ck: please give comment on the timing of this line, should i separate the "Say" or should i not lol}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.55,0:15:31.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's something I'd like to ask you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.22,0:15:32.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.17,0:15:38.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though Jin and you are siblings, you hadn't met each other until recently, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.50,0:15:45.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've both reached {\i1}that{\i0} age, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.47,0:15:47.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Living under the same roof would mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.71,0:15:49.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nagi-san, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.65,0:15:53.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How do you feel about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.77,0:16:02.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.04,0:16:05.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I just think you're so cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.54,0:16:08.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jin-kun is just a child to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.94,0:16:10.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We live together, that's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.62,0:16:11.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We are family.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.36,0:16:17.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why there's nothing for you to be worried about.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.03,0:16:19.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not what I meant...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.47,0:16:24.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way we can be in a relationship.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.16,0:16:27.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're an important person to Jin-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.14,0:16:30.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.89,0:16:34.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have somebody that I like.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.43,0:16:41.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who would have thought you have such a complex situation in your family.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.76,0:16:44.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But don't worry about it, Mikuriya.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.04,0:16:46.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This kind of situation turns up often in comics!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.61,0:16:47.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Comic, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.44,0:16:50.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That one, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.11,0:16:55.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you're not a student, and you're a girl, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.61,0:16:57.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to go to a place with ghosts...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.69,0:17:02.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I like supernatural phenomenon.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.22,0:17:04.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fanatic?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.14,0:17:06.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I do have some exorcism skills myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.35,0:17:09.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it, living in an enclosed environment makes one twisted.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.27,0:17:11.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry, Mikuriya.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.48,0:17:15.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are precedents of wealthy girls with a fetish for the supernatural.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.45,0:17:16.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In a girl game. {to editor: galge = gal game. erotic game. hentai game}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.17,0:17:16.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're talking about a girl game?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.36,0:17:18.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.58,0:17:21.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She put her purification staff in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.43,0:17:25.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You! You took that from my drawer without asking!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.60,0:17:27.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes? You mean this bag?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.71,0:17:30.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you not to open my drawers without my permission!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.18,0:17:31.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.43,0:17:33.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No real reason...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.20,0:17:36.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as you think nothing of it...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.76,0:17:39.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I thought nothing of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.61,0:17:41.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Although I did think that you like big boobs.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.55,0:17:42.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you saw everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.20,0:17:44.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say that! Tsugumi is here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.88,0:17:47.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I heard this is natural for a healthy male,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.28,0:17:49.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so you don't need to feel bothered-
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.79,0:17:50.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.73,0:18:01.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.25,0:18:03.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,let's charge in!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.93,0:18:05.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.64,0:18:07.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jin, that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.39,0:18:09.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, even I can't give you a proper answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.89,0:18:13.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah... Isn't that stick from the anime series that got scrapped in the planning stage,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.45,0:18:16.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and only its goods are sold by the sponsor's toy company?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.55,0:18:18.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}There's a craze over it and they're sold over the net at high prices.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.78,0:18:18.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Akiba? Your eyes changed color.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.69,0:18:25.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.01,0:18:39.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The air is certainly stagnant.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.68,0:18:42.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If there's an impurity here, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.38,0:18:44.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.73,0:18:45.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The place with the ghost...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.21,0:18:47.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's here, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.70,0:18:48.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's open it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.10,0:18:51.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.26,0:18:52.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, let's go back instead!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.58,0:18:54.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You may get cursed! I feel bad for the ghosts!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.75,0:18:58.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As a matter of fact... I've reached the limit of my endurance.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.05,0:19:03.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Daitetsu-kun has gone mad from fear and he's crushing Jin!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.98,0:19:05.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're so loud. Stop that ruckus!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.19,0:19:09.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You people are humans, aren't you? You're the living.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.02,0:19:11.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have a future, you are the best,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.92,0:19:14.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,there's no reason for you to lose to creatures that move because they're bound to their past!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.28,0:19:16.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Her way of speaking...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.47,0:19:17.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She has taken on that personality.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.08,0:19:20.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The living is stronger than the dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.16,0:19:20.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Remember that!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.03,0:19:24.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? No way! What's that? Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.87,0:19:26.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't open it! I can't open it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.25,0:19:34.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's coming. It seems we've agitated it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.03,0:19:36.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's angry!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.66,0:19:39.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's certainly calling for help.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.20,0:19:43.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Poor thing... It was always alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.02,0:19:46.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was in such a dark place, hurting and afraid.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.38,0:19:49.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And yet nobody could find him.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.32,0:19:52.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He can't open that door for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.42,0:19:56.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because he was caught in the maze of dying without being able to open the door.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.01,0:20:00.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I shall destroy that maze.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.13,0:20:12.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh sheesh...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.09,0:20:15.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This door is poorly built, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.89,0:20:23.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is dangerous. I should tell the school janitor to fix it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.74,0:20:25.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's this old man?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.48,0:20:27.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Old man? You're so rude.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.50,0:20:28.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's that person?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.55,0:20:29.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Homeless?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.43,0:20:32.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yay, yay! Gotcha!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.60,0:20:36.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we don't do this, I don't feel like we're welcoming the new members at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.82,0:20:39.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This sort of thing happens often in sport clubs, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.13,0:20:40.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is what they call a baptism.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.24,0:20:42.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me introduce him.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.33,0:20:45.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is our Arts Club's advisor, Dokusasori-sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.00,0:20:47.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's using the place under the floor as his studio.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.70,0:20:50.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys don't learn your lesson, doing this every year.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.19,0:20:53.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I don't mind since I enjoy it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.44,0:20:57.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys were so scared!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.75,0:20:59.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps I should have taped it on video.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.86,0:21:02.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.11,0:21:02.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, who is this beauty?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.86,0:21:06.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's the impurity?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.98,0:21:08.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's the bug?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.00,0:21:12.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bug? There are lots of them here, big ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.91,0:21:14.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big spiders...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.56,0:21:16.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's more over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.91,0:21:19.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nagi-
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.29,0:21:27.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nagi-san, where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.52,0:21:30.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That can't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.54,0:21:32.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That can't be, That can't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.59,0:21:35.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure I sensed an impurity!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.54,0:21:46.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My senses are failing.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.59,0:21:50.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A place of worship...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.37,0:21:53.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A place for propagating religion?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.94,0:21:55.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't notice.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.77,0:22:05.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Goal! {I came}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.60,0:22:10.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You fail the test if it comes with a time limit though.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.22,0:22:14.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were searching in such a wrong place.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.01,0:22:16.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.65,0:22:20.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Without that toy, you can't clean up on your own?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.81,0:22:25.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Has your divinity diminished?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.15,0:22:26.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.87,0:22:28.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.40,0:22:31.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.74,0:22:33.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big Sis.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.02,0:23:39.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please watch the next episode of Kannagi too!
